'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2915] on 12 November 2000 at 5:51:50 pm'!"Change Set:		244NewSymbolTable6-sqrDate:			30 August 2000Author:			Andres ValloudRemoves old symbol tables (and the system keeps working after that).Added Symbol>>compactSymbolTables. Utility method that will crunch the symbol tables to a barely acceptable size"!String variableByteSubclass: #Symbol	instanceVariableNames: ''	classVariableNames: 'SymbolTable '	poolDictionaries: ''	category: 'Collections-Text'!!Symbol class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'SqR 8/30/2000 13:59'!compactSymbolTable	"Reduce the size of the symbol table so	that it holds all existing symbols + 1000"	| oldSize |	Smalltalk garbageCollect.	oldSize _ SymbolTable array size.	SymbolTable growTo: SymbolTable slowSize + 1000.	^(oldSize - SymbolTable array size) printString, ' slot(s) reclaimed'! !"Postscript:Compact the symbol table"Transcript 	cr; show: 'Several symbol tables removed.';	cr; show: Symbol compactSymbolTable!